Yarta
-----

This is the Yarta source tree which is organized as follows:

- root
	+ docs (contains documentation & useful information to read before proceeding in using)
	+ external (here you should place all the external libraries needed for compiling);
	+ misc (contains two old projects: DataExtractionDemo & PolicyManager)
	- mselib
		+ libapps (contains library project applications which will contain
			heavy implementation for different objects such as kbservice, etc.)
		+ MSE-Middleware (the actual mse library)
	+ samples (contains sample applications using Yarta library)
	+ tools (contains developer tools used for developing apps using Yarta)
	

