For guidance on getting the required libraries you can browse the following links:

Apache Velocity 1.7 (Apache 2.0)
Download : http://velocity.apache.org/download.cgi

Apache Jena 2.6.2 - includes arq 2.8.1, iri 0.7, log4j 1.2.13 (Apache 2.0)
Download : http://www.apache.org/dist/jena/binaries/

Androjena 1.0 (Apache 2.0)
Download : https://code.google.com/p/androjena/

Facebook4J (Apache 2.0)
Download : http://facebook4j.org/

Twitter4J (Apache 2.0)
Download : http://twitter4j.org

Linkedin-J (Apache 2.0)
Download : https://code.google.com/p/linkedin-j/

Google Analytics (Apache 2.0)
Download : https://code.google.com/p/google-api-java-client/wiki/APIs#Google_Analytics_API

Ibicoop (Ambientic SAS)
Contact : contact@ambientic.com, http://www.ambientic.com/en/#contact

Building with ANT
-----------------

In order to build the project using ant, please modify the following build variables in local.properties:

- Signatures Location

Also, you need to have ANDROID_HOME, JAVA_HOME environment variables set correctly.

Building with Eclipse
---------------------

Manually copy everything from /external/android to /mselib/libapps/android/YartaLibrary/libs.
